Responsibilities
Support the Finance team in:

  Researching and applying relevant analysis tools and techniques on financial information to provide value-added financial insights to support the organisation’s plans as well as effective internal control.
Using data visualisation tools (eg, Microstrategy) to develop dashboards and infographics for financial data.

Qualifications

  Qualifications with a major in data management and analysis.
  Proficient in data sorting and analysis tools such as Access, Excel or BI.
  Strong quantitative and analytical skill and statistics knowledge.
  Good written and presentation skills.


The successful candidate will be appointed on a 1 year traineeship agreement.

We regret to inform only successful candidates will be notified.
